{d^2y\over dx^2}={d\over dx}{dy\over dx}={d\over dx}(\cos y-\sin y)^{-1}=-(\cos y-\sin y)^{-2}\cdot\Bigl[ (-\sin y){dy\over dx} -(\cos y){dy\over dx}\Bigr].
